text: Yvonne Stoffel-Wagener (16 May 1931 - 5 April 2014) was a Luxembourgian gymnast. She competed in five events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:2014 deaths Category:Luxembourgian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Luxembourg Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Esch-sur-Alzette
